title: Snaps - Week 8 Reaction: Texas A&M loses, LSU beats Ole Miss, Oregon wins, Clemson Survives
itunes:title: Snaps - Week 8 Reaction: Texas A&M loses, LSU beats Ole Miss, Oregon wins, Clemson Survives
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert react to another wild Saturday of college football including Jimbo Fisher & Texas A&M falling to 3-4, LSU upsets Ole Miss 45-20, Oregon rolling UCLA 45-30, and Clemson surviving against Syracuse 28-21 and much more! #Volume #herd #colincowherd
